Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:38.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had caught a terrible cold{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:40.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and returned to the present-day world\nto get better.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:46.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}All my friends came to\nvisit me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:50.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But then, I learned about the\ntest the following day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:55.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo, please help me study!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:57.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But my feverjust wouldn't\ngo down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:00.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just when I thought\NI wouldn't make it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:02.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here. Medicine. Drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:05.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to the potion that Inuyasha\nmade for me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:07.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was able to get through\nthe test somehow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The weather's great\nand I feel great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:36.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm overmy cold... and I made\nit through the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:39.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:43.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:45.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:49.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're that much better,\nlet's justgo on back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:51.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:54.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:55.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:06.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Why must I come along\nwith you forthis?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:09.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll be going on a long journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so we have to stock up\non supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:15.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Last time, didn't you tell me\NNOTto go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:17.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was then, this is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:22.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:30.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When we're walking like this,\nit's as though we're on a date.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:37.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Kagome!\NThese are all edible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:47.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay Inuyasha,\nwhat do you want most?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ninja food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:01.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Instant noodles are...\noverthere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:02.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:10.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:14.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's hard to choose...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe we bought too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's an understatement!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:38.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid! Don't stop so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- That's...\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, why're we hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:53.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Sota. I wonderwhat he's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A present, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:59.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Found something you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-When you've decided, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:30.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:36.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His foot slipped into the pail\nand he fell into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:40.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yourpoor father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:43.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's his fault forbeing so clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He didn't get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:46.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, just a huge lump on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:53.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:14.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sota?\NNo appetite?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:17.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-uh... it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:20.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At times like this, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:23.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A scale from a mermaid...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,passed down through\ngenerations of Higurashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:28.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tape this scale onto yournavel\nand sleep with it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and amazingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Buyo, you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:41.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Hey wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's from a mermaid!\NNo kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:48.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe he's not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:49.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:50.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- What?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:53.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a sickness...\NIove sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:55.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Love sickness?\N- Love sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:58.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well now, I'll have to make red-bean\nrice to mark this milestone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:02.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know! I'll use that as a reason for\nyournext absence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Your teacherwill be fooled.\N- He will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a wonderful sickness to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:19.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can I talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:23.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An important talk, man to man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you don't have anything to say,\NI'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:43.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:46.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?\NHurry up and speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:49.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is love eternal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:53.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's this,\nall of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:54.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:57.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who said, "I love you" first?\NYou or Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:02.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:05.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, you're boyfriend and\ngirlfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:06.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you weren't her boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis wouldn't skip school to\nvisit your time and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:16.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you wouldn't come here\nto take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:17.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So tell me, who said it first?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How did you declare yourlove?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if I'd say that to Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:29.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then did Kagome tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:30.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:37.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or maybe, neither of you\nhave said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:39.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-W-W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:40.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You haven't, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:46.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:50.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:53.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like I know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:57.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hername is Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't ask!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:06.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hitomi is in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:10.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And she sits next to me\nin the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:21.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like I should talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:24.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But she's very cute with\nbig, round eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:26.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And she's fair and used\nto live abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:27.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And doesn't like parsley.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And she doesn't carry\na backpack...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't understand\nall of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:33.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But in otherwords,\nyou love this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:37.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:42.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I don't know how\NHitomi feels about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:44.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to declare my\nlove to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:51.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W- Why must he tell\nme all this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:55.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can I practice with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:03.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me practice declaring\nmy love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,J-Just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:15.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:34.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NHurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to prepare myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:39.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're notgonna say it,\NI'm going inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:41.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:59.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:02.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I... love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:17.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't have to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:23.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come\nto me from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:28.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm much wiser about a girl's\nfeelings than Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:31.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Course, you're a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:37.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll show you how!\N'Cuz you're my dear little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:48.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:52.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perfect. It'll be all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:55.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:56.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:57.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:00.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,During lunch break, allude to\nyourfeelings ever so slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:02.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then after class, call Hitomi out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and when you're all alone,\nmake yourdeclaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:08.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to stay in this get-up\nand go to class until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And what's so bad about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:11.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is an important moment\nin yourlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:16.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do yourbest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:19.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota Higurashi! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, you say it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:28.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:30.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Declaration?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:38.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, a declaration!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:40.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, did Hojo tell you\nhe loves you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:43.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that's why you look\nso happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:46.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you'll be two-timing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Not Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:54.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're saying that other guy\nhasn't declared his love foryou yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd betterget that straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:58.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can cause problems later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:01.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about me.\NIt's Sota!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:05.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:07.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean, yourkid brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:12.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. He's going to declare his\nlove in school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:13.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder how he'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She seems so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:18.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:22.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say! So different from\nthe usual Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:33.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jilted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:36.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:39.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:42.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yourplan probably\ndidn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:46.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:58.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Sota...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}T- This hopeless look...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No mistake...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:14.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been jilted!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:23.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota... cheerup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit acting so depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There're lotsa otherwomen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:30.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:35.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wasn't jilted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:40.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:42.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Couldn't tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:47.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just like you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:50.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I called Hitomi out after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:53.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sota?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:56.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:15:00.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you don't have anything to say,\NI'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:02.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh... Just a minute, Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:05.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:13.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:17.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:21.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I lo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:27.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:28.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:32.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't like men who can't\nspeak up clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:41.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the end forme!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:44.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's what happened?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:48.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You haven'teven told heryet.\NSo quit crying like a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the same as being jilted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:54.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a weakling and I'm not worthy.\NAnd I can't speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:57.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then YOU have to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:03.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NI'll make you strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:04.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:13.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:14.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:22.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good! Not bad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:24.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:26.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:27.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:30.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:34.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you trying to do\nwith him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:36.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is all a matter of spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:39.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as Sota gets into\nthe spirit of doing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:40.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that's all that's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:43.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:44.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:47.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... Just talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y'know Sota...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I maybe imagining it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but that training you just did\nseems to be building up your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:54.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:57.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think you've gotten\na bit stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:16:59.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're definitely a\ndifferent Sota from awhile ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:05.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You see, Sota?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:06.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So do yourbest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:17.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Banzai! Banzai! Banzai! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:20.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Banzai! Banzai!\N- Why even Grandpa and Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:24.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nevermind. Just do your best, Sota.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:28.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I feel like I've been tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:30.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Banzai! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:32.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:37.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Man! This is harderthan\nexterminating demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:42.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still... what an indecisive kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:46.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so disappointed\nin my youngerbrother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:50.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mulling overthe problem like\nthat isn'tgonna solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:54.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say. If he loves her,\nhe should just say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:00.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:09.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you came back\nwith your tail between yourlegs?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:10.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Afterthinking about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:15.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I realized that just a little\ntraining isn'tgoing to make me strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't change my character\nthateasily!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oops... He figured it out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it all!\NWill you cut this out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:29.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop dawdling like this!\NGo and settle it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:34.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit making excuses!\NC'mere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:42.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now listen up, Sota.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until you tell her,\ndon't come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:48.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you come back without\ntelling her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you won't be allowed inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}my{\i0} house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Spirit! It's all in the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:57.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Make up your mind!\NThat's all it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:58.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn, what a weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:04.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota! Didn't you say\nyou love her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:08.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:10.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pluck up your courage\nand go forit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:18.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:19.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:20.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do yourbest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:27.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:30.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to watch over him.\NAs his big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:32.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:34.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:51.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NYou seem sorta different today, Sota.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:53.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:57.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have something important\nto tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aren't you a man?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:14.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pluck up yourcourage\nand go forit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:17.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hitomi, I'm not strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:24.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I'm an indecisive person\nwho can't speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:26.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I really like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:38.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you be my girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:50.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:54.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:10.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-They're only in\nthe third grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:12.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,P-Pretty good, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:39.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One... two... three...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:42.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing forgotten, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:44.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Kay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:45.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:47.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See ya, Sota.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:49.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:51.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:55.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:56.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:57.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:02.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:05.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:06.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:51.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? What're you looking for, Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:53.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kuroro, who lived in Koume's village.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.48,0:23:56.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A strange faith healerhad her\nbanned from the village
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:58.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,saying she brought bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:24:00.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kuroro resembles Kirara and\nshe's very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:02.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cats are natural enemies of rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:06.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe this is connected to the village\nbeing overrun by a huge pack of rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:10.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.53,0:24:12.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"The Suspicious Faith Healer\nand the Black Kirara"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.79,0:24:14.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take care of things here!
